---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Arhum Savera">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Senior Software Engineer with 7+ years building backend platforms,
      machine learning systems, and production AI workflows.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-profile">
      <div class="about-photo-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/arhumsavera-profile.png"
          alt="Portrait of Arhum Savera"
          class="about-photo"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="panel about-intro">
        <h2>Building Practical AI Systems</h2>
        <p>
          I focus on AI platforms that can hold up in production: observable
          orchestration runtimes, reliable memory systems, and tooling that
          keeps operators in control.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work sits at the intersection of backend engineering, applied ML,
          and product execution, with a strong bias toward systems that are
          measurable, debuggable, and useful beyond demos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What I&rsquo;ve Been Building (February 2026)</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Voice Coding Workflow</h3>
        <p>Local speech interface for coding with low-latency transcription and spoken response hooks.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Agentic Task Orchestration</h3>
        <p>Multi-step orchestration runtime with domain-aware routing, reusable tool chains, and traceable execution.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Agent Memory</h3>
        <p>Shared memory framework with semantic, episodic, and procedural layers for reliable context retention.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Source-Grounded Context</h3>
        <p>Structured source data pipelines so generated outputs stay tied to real project history.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Now</h2>
    <div class="panel">
      <p>
        I am focused on local-first AI systems that improve real engineering workflows
        through faster iteration loops, stronger context retention, and dependable orchestration.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Timeline</h2>
    <div class="panel">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>2026:</strong> Local-first agent tooling (voice workflows, memory systems, and orchestration).</li>
        <li><strong>2020:</strong> Amazon Dash Cart vision pipelines, edge optimization, and production operations.</li>
        <li><strong>2017:</strong> Signify LightFinder deep learning and retrieval systems.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-profile {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    grid-template-columns: 280px minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .about-photo-wrap {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, #171f2be0, #0f141cf2);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 340px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-intro h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.2vw, 1.8rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .about-profile {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-photo {
      min-height: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
